        .col-lg-6.img.col-sm-12.pull-right
          img(src="landing-assets/img/aboutmrktplce.png")
          h3 Buy from others
          p.col-lg-12 Buy second-hand gear from those who share the same outdoor passion with you. 
      .col-lg-10.col-lg-offset-1.about
        .col-lg-6.img.col-sm-12.img
          img(src="landing-assets/img/aboutreview.png")
          h3 Review gear
          p.col-lg-12 Post reviews on outdoor gear you have used. Share your knowledge and experience with others. 
        .col-lg-6.img.col-sm-12.img.pull-right
